contentrichtext.text: {{Wiktionary|libera}} '''Libera''' may refer to: * [[Libera (mythology)]], a Roman goddess of fertility * [[Libera (music)]], a boy vocal group from London * [[Libera (song)|''Libera'' (song)]], a song by Italian artist Mia Martini * [[Libera (gastropod)|''Libera'' (gastropod)]], a genus of gastropods in the family Endodontidae * [[Adalberto Libera]], an Italian architect (1903-1963) == See also == * ''[[Libera me]]'' ("Deliver me"), a Roman Catholic responsory that is sung in the Office of the Dead {{disambiguation}}
